Miss Heliotrop, I'm fine!

25
00:04:08,147 --> 00:04:09,048
Really!

26
00:04:13,019 --> 00:04:13,720
Yes...

27
00:04:57,697 --> 00:04:59,232
"Once upon a perfect time...

28
00:05:00,867 --> 00:05:02,368
many hundreds of years ago...

29
00:05:03,036 --> 00:05:05,838
when the old magic called
Moonacre Valley...

30
