Stop! Stop...
I don't want to hear another word!

366
00:37:54,705 --> 00:37:56,007
You are all insane!!

367
00:38:03,247 --> 00:38:08,419
Three hundred and eighty-four years...

368
00:38:10,988 --> 00:38:15,593
times thirteen for the moon's per annum.

369
00:38:17,194 --> 00:38:18,529
Plus...

370
00:38:22,667 --> 00:38:25,102
seven moons for this year.

371
00:38:26,637 --> 00:38:27,938
That's...

372
00:38:31,475 --> 00:38:33,344
That makes...

373
00:38:35,713 --> 00:38:38,149
four thousand nine hundred
and ninety-nine.

374
00:38:39,517 --> 00:38:43,654
Oh Serena, the very next moon's
arrival will be the 5,000th moon.

375
00:38:45,890 --> 00:38:47,525
Everyone knows the legend...

376
00:38:47,892 --> 00:38:49,694
These pearls belongs to no man...

377
00:38:50,027 --> 00:38:51,062
They belong to nature!

378
00:38:51,228 --> 00:38:53,931
5,000 moons to set it right!!

379
00:38:54,632 --> 00:38:57,868
You're a Merryweather...

380
00:38:57,902 --> 00:38:59,904
You're the chosen one!

381
00:39:05,343 --> 00:39:07,211
Keep out of the forest child!

382
00:39:25,930 --> 00:39:28,432
I've to get out of this
remote place, Serena!

383
00:39:28,532 --> 00:39:31,168
I don't want anything more
to do with this!

384
00:39:33,237 --> 00:39:35,773
Miss Heliotrope
will take good care of you.

385
00:39:59,029 --> 00:40:00,498
Maria....

386
00:40:05,736 --> 00:40:07,471
Maria...

387
00:40:23,220 --> 00:40:24,388
Who are you?

388
00:40:32,797 --> 00:40:36,333
You look...
just like the lady in the painting.

389
00:40:37,635 --> 00:40:39,170
Come along.

390
00:40:49,447 --> 00:40:51,015
Oh, do come in!!

391
00:40:58,889 --> 00:41:00,424
You naughty hedgehog!

392
00:41:00,658 --> 00:41:03,060
In my favorite chair again!

393
00:41:03,894 --> 00:41:05,629
You cheeky monkey!

394
00:41:10,868 --> 00:41:12,002
Be nice and still,

395
00:41:12,169 --> 00:41:14,071
don't make any sudden movement.

396
00:41:14,305 --> 00:41:15,840
Then she won't be so scared!

397
00:41:16,373 --> 00:41:17,641
I will try!

398
00:41:18,576 --> 00:41:20,644
Oh! I was talking to the snake.

399
00:41:22,446 --> 00:41:25,616
I rescued as many
injured creatures as I can.

400
00:41:29,153 --> 00:41:30,517
And did you do the embroidery

401
00:41:30,518 --> 00:41:32,823
and brought all those
strange dresses in my room?

402
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:34,291
Yes.

403
00:41:36,961 --> 00:41:38,429
My name is Loveday.

404
00:41:50,941 --> 00:42:10,551
Our time is nearly spent right here...
the moon shall not be our forever.

405
00:42:17,501 --> 00:42:19,373
You saw something,
didn't you?

406
00:42:19,374 --> 00:42:21,305
Didn't you?
Tell me what you saw.

407
00:42:21,338 --> 00:42:22,506
I have to leave!

408
00:42:22,606 --> 00:42:24,124
No no no no...

409
00:42:24,159 --> 00:42:25,643
Stay with me!

410
00:42:26,443 --> 00:42:27,978
I've frightened you, haven't I?

411
00:42:28,145 --> 00:42:30,648
You see,
I'm not used to visitors.

412
00:42:30,981 --> 00:42:33,183
And I do so much just
want to be your friend.

413
00:42:34,018 --> 00:42:36,387
