picked up the box!

467
00:48:08,051 --> 00:48:10,120
They stole the pearls.

468
00:48:11,221 --> 00:48:13,023
But soon...

469
00:48:13,257 --> 00:48:15,859
the final moon will rise...

470
00:48:16,260 --> 00:48:19,897
and the thieving Merryweathers
will be punished!

471
00:48:21,098 --> 00:48:23,700
I'm glad that we have you here.

472
00:48:24,067 --> 00:48:26,770
There's nothing anyone can do to stop it!

473
00:48:27,304 --> 00:48:31,208
At last the entire valley will be ours!

474
00:48:32,609 --> 00:48:37,481
And the De Noir will finally
feast upon revenge!!

475
00:48:52,629 --> 00:48:54,464
Leave me alone, you ogre!

476
00:48:55,365 --> 00:48:57,265
You know,
for someone in your predicament,

477
00:48:57,266 --> 00:48:58,502
I have to admire your spirit!

478
00:49:04,541 --> 00:49:05,175
Witch!

479
00:49:08,211 --> 00:49:09,513
Hey!
Lock her in!

480
00:49:10,847 --> 00:49:13,350
Welcome to your new house!!

481
00:49:13,650 --> 00:49:15,552
Hope you make friends
with the roaches!

482
00:49:20,023 --> 00:49:22,225
Guard, watch her...
she's slippery.

483
00:49:55,392 --> 00:49:57,527
Where is that girl?

484
00:49:57,928 --> 00:49:58,996
Unbelievable!

485
00:50:07,771 --> 00:50:08,972
Absolutely irresponsible!

486
00:51:07,731 --> 00:51:09,633
Oh, this dress!

487
00:51:40,163 --> 00:51:42,065
Come back here, you witch!!!

488
00:51:43,100 --> 00:51:44,067
