- Let's try north!

493
00:53:22,465 --> 00:53:23,700
Go Robin, find her!

494
00:53:28,772 --> 00:53:30,440
I want her killed!

495
00:53:31,775 --> 00:53:33,843
I want her to stop the curse.

496
00:53:34,311 --> 00:53:37,881
Their death is our victory!

497
00:53:39,616 --> 00:53:42,252
Stupid girl...
should have stayed where you were.

498
00:54:05,742 --> 00:54:06,610
Robin!

499
00:54:33,670 --> 00:54:34,337
This way!

500
00:54:42,112 --> 00:54:43,813
Oh... Wolf!!

501
00:54:48,952 --> 00:54:51,621
Quickly!
