00:55:31,394 --> 00:55:32,329
Miss Heliotrop!

508
00:55:33,063 --> 00:55:33,863
Miss Heliotrop!

509
00:55:34,831 --> 00:55:36,066
I'm perfectly alright...
yes.

510
00:55:36,966 --> 00:55:39,402
