00:55:56,419 --> 00:55:58,521
Go upstairs this instance
and tidy yourself up!

519
00:55:59,589 --> 00:55:59,856
But...

520
00:56:00,056 --> 00:56:01,491
Just do as you're told!

521
00:56:06,663 --> 00:56:09,833
You're not my father!

522
00:56:23,646 --> 00:56:24,180
Maria!

523
00:56:25,181 --> 00:56:26,383
Maria, open this door!

524
00:56:28,351 --> 00:56:29,352
Listen...

525
00:56:30,787 --> 00:56:35,258
It maybe possible...
that I was... a little rough earlier.

526
00:56:35,425 --> 00:56:37,861
The point is you were gone
for such a long time.

527
00:56:38,395 --> 00:56:40,230
I mean you didn't even tell us!

528
00:56:40,830 --> 00:56:41,364
I...

